name: osteotomy
description: @tivonrice www.tivonrice.com - Otherwise known as "The Gates of Hell" or just "Poochie" - Tivon Rice's dog is asleep on the job. Actually, being asleep is the job. There's snoring on the soundtrack as the dog's long, flat tongue flutters behind the broken-picket fence of its wet, white teeth. The video is an example of the "malignant-benign". The dog is napping (benign), but his mouth looks like a tunnel of death (malignant) at a carnival, accompanied by drool.
